Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
When I'm go to Page 01 of Mammography/ Breast ultrasound
When I select 'Lumps / hardening in the breast detected' from the dropdown menu of Indikation / Beschwerden
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And	'Since when?' dropdown menu is enabled
And	a single choice Localization figure is enabled
When I select '1 Month' from 'Since when?' dropdown menu
And	I select 'R' on the Localization figure
Then 'R' part turns red
When I select 'L' on the Localization figure
Then 'L' part turns red
And	'R' part turns white
